<lb ed="I" n="0203a03" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0203a04" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0203a05" type="honorific"/>淨信佛主　　　　　　　除疑<note n="0203002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30995"/>＝冥【史】</note><app n="0203002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30995"/></rdg></app>佛主陳黑　　　　　花色王佛主清信張舍妃　菩提華佛主清信荊元妃　　<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>上流<app type="star" corresp="#0203001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩀌</rdg></app>光佛主陳洪興　　　　　　　<note n="0203003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨳰＝開【史】</note><app n="0203003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">開</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨳰</rdg></app>日月光佛主陳洪度
